description: Try our easy to follow Easter Basket Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Easter Basket Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Add 3 or 4 drops of green food colouring to shredded coconut and toss to tint. Decorate top of cake with a nest of green coconut and top with coloured Easter eggs.
